        <h2 class="h4 mb-3">3. External data sources and services</h2>
        <p class="mb-3">The site fetches external data during build and also uses a few external services in the interface. Some sources are cached and mirrored into local fallback files so the site can still build when a source is unavailable.</p>
        <div class="table-responsive mb-3">
          <table class="table table-hover align-middle">
            <thead>
              <tr>
                <th>API / Database</th>
                <th>Provider</th>
                <th>Usage on this site</th>
              </tr>
            </thead>
            <tbody>
              <tr>
                <td><strong>Canva Connect API</strong></td>
                <td>Canva</td>
                <td>Canva presentation metadata for presentation listings.</td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td><strong>Canva analysis pipeline</strong></td>
                <td>Canva + Node scripts + AI-assisted synthesis</td>
                <td>Canva presentation data is normalized, enriched, and condensed before being turned into the analysis page.</td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td><strong>Finna API</strong></td>
                <td>National Library of Finland (Finna)</td>
                <td>Library, archive and museum records on the Finna page.</td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td><strong>GitHub API</strong></td>
                <td>GitHub, Inc.</td>
                <td>Site change log table from repository commits.</td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td><strong>OpenAlex API</strong></td>
                <td>OurResearch</td>
                <td>Citation and profile metrics.</td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td><strong>Oulu open data API</strong><br><code>city_council_meeting_videos</code></td>
                <td>City of Oulu</td>
                <td>City council meeting videos on politics pages.</td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td><strong>OuluREPO OpenSearch</strong></td>
                <td>University of Oulu</td>
                <td>Supervised theses and reviewed thesis records.</td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td><strong>Research.fi API</strong></td>
                <td>Ministry of Education and Culture / CSC</td>
                <td>Scientific publication data on publication and writing views.</td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td><strong>Semantic Scholar API</strong></td>
                <td>Allen Institute for AI</td>
